title: Infinity The Hunt 01 (of 4) (2013) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description: Hank Pym, Wolverine, and She-Hulk bring the students of the Marvel Universe together to announce a new CONTEST OF CHAMPIONS!This CONTEST OF CHAMPIONS pits the super students of schools all over the Marvel U (including some you've never seen before) against each other.However, the Contest is interrupted when Thanos' forces descend on Earth. What do they have to do with the young heroes?
